art%27s_Home\" title=\"Heart&#39;s Home\">Heart's Home</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Ironoaks</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Longbow_Hall\" title=\"Longbow Hall\">Longbow Hall</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Newkeep\" title=\"Newkeep\">Newkeep</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Ninestars\" title=\"Ninestars\">Ninestars</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Old_Anchor\" title=\"Old Anchor\">Old Anchor</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Redfort\" title=\"Redfort\">Redfort</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Runestone\" title=\"Runestone\">Runestone</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Sisterton\" title=\"Sisterton\">Sisterton</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Snakewood\" title=\"Snakewood\">Snakewood</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Strongsong\" title=\"Strongsong\">Strongsong</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Wickenden\" title=\"Wickenden\">Wickenden</a></li></ul>\n</div></td></tr><tr style=\"height:2px\"><td></td></tr><tr><td scope=\"row\" class=\"navbox-group\" style=\";;\">Locations</td><td style=\"text-align:left;border-left-width:2px;border-left-style:solid;width:100%;padding:0px;;;\" class=\"navbox-list navbox-even\"><div style=\"padding:0em 0.25em\">\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Alyssa%27s_Tears\" title=\"Alyssa&#39;s Tears\">Alyssa's Tears</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Bay_of_Crabs\" title=\"Bay of Crabs\">Bay of Crabs</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Bite\" title=\"Bite\">Bite</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Fingers\" title=\"Fingers\">Fingers</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Giant%27s_Lance\" title=\"Giant&#39;s Lance\">Giant's Lance</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Headman%27s_Mount\" title=\"Headman&#39;s Mount\">Headman's Mount</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/High_road\" title=\"High road\">High Road</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Mountains_of_the_Moon\" title=\"Mountains of the Moon\">Mountains of the Moon</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Paps\" title=\"Paps\">Paps</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Pebble\